<section class="hero">

<h1>
Lipid<span>omics</span>
</h1>

<p>
Lipidomics investigates the diverse lipid molecules that shape membranes, signaling pathways, energy storage, inflammation, metabolism, and cellular identity. By profiling lipid species and lipid networks, lipidomics reveals how biochemical regulation influences health, disease, and therapeutic response.
</p>

<div class="hero-image">
  <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
    <source src="/3_Lipidomics.mp4" type="video/mp4">
