<section class="section">

<h2>
What is <span>Lipidomics?</span>
</h2>

<div class="infographic">

  <img
    src="/1_Lipidomics.png"
    alt="Lipidomics overview infographic"
  >

</div>

<p>
Lipidomics is the comprehensive study of lipid molecules and lipid-related pathways across cells, tissues, organisms, and biological systems.
</p>

<p>
Modern lipidomics uses mass spectrometry, computational lipid annotation, pathway analysis, and systems biology to understand membrane biology, metabolic regulation, inflammation, disease mechanisms, and therapeutic response.
</p>

