Lipidomics and <span>Omics Sciences</span>
</h2>

<p>
Lipidomics connects metabolism, membrane biology, signaling, and disease mechanisms by measuring lipid species that influence cellular behavior and physiological function.
</p>

<p>
At PanorOmics, lipidomics is a critical omics layer for understanding biochemical regulation, cellular communication, metabolic health, inflammation, and translational biotechnology.
